      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine<strong> half </strong>of your <strong>pesto </strong>(you’ll use the rest later!) with your <strong>mayo </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>pesto mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
