    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>remaining pesto</strong> with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> in a large bowl – this is your<strong> pesto dressing</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> into wedges</p>",
